    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Focus timer with customizable work and break intervals. Auto-transitions between sessions with sound alerts and visual progress tracking.</p>

    <%# Ad: leaderboard — placed below content heading per AdSense best practices %>
